{1: '1', 2: 'Young Lad', 3: "Where do you think you're going!", 4: '1'}
{3: "The young lad blocks the rebels' escape and knocks over their chieftain."}
{3: 'Seeing their leader fall, the thieves kneel down in fright and surrender.'}
{3: 'Only the young lad clad in an black robe stands resolute on the stage to a round of resounding applause.'}
{3: 'This is just another night in Kowloong, way back in the past...'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory67.jpg'}
{2: 'System Notice', 3: 'Record recovery over.'}
{2: 'Huaxu', 3: 'Unable to determine why "she" would want to access such data.'}
{3: 'Huaxu shows a brief pause in response.'}
{3: 'It might have been to do with having a new master. Or perhaps Huaxu has yet to adapt to the way she handles things.'}
{2: 'Huaxu', 3: 'Even for the purpose of "studying humanity", it\'s unknown as to why one would access such a wide range of data.'}
{3: 'At this moment, Huaxu is floating in the center of a virtual space, and in front... are the data nodes that "she" has requested for.'}
{2: 'Huaxu', 3: 'But... I will carry out the commands.'}
{3: 'Huaxu waves, sending data to the place to the output node.'}
{2: 'Huaxu', 3: 'Broadcast accessed data.'}
{3: 'Because Huaxu is an AI.'}
{3: "And an AI's prerogative is determined by its creator."}
{3: "As long as this is the master's wish, an AI will do everything to fulfill the master's will."}
{2: 'Huaxu', 3: 'Now processing the next command.'}
